Usage: waldo.py [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...

  Puppeteering tool for animatronics.

Options:
  -p  --play projectname [start]
                         Playback of every servo in projectname and,
                         if existent, audio, fom startpoint [start]
  -sp --singleplay projectname channelfilename [audiofilename]
                         Playback of one specific servo though a specific
                         servo. Optional audioplayback.
  -r  --record projectname channelfilename servopin [audiofilename]
                         Record channelfilename for servopin. Optional
                         audioplayback.
  -c  --connection projectname
                         Set connection type (USB/MCP3008).
  -n  --new projectname	 Create new project structure.
  -ls --list             List evey project and every channel with their
                         ServoHAT-pin-associations.
  -cc --copy             Show copyright infos.
  -h  --help             Show this message and exit.